title: Coolie
subTitle: Seema, the daughter of a wealthy businessman, falls in love with a labourer. However, complications arise when Seema's father refuses to accept their relationship.

title: Shagird
subTitle: Professor Brij, who is sworn to bachelorhood, mentors Ramesh, who wants to be just like him. However, when the professor falls for Poonam, he faces a dilemma.

title: Khushboo
subTitle: Kusum and Brindavan get married as children but are separated due to a misunderstanding. Years later, they cross paths again and try to fix their relationship.

subTitle: Bharti, a young girl studying law, belongs to a rich family. All hell breaks loose when she discovers the truth about her father's methods of amassing wealth.

title: Baseraa
subTitle: Nima and Balraj's life is thrown out of gear when her sister and Balraj's first wife, Sharada, returns home after spending 14 years in a mental asylum.

title: Teesri Aankh
subTitle: Mali brings up an orphan baby boy as her own. Later, when her husband reveals the real identity of the child, she strives to cope with the truth.

title: Rajput
subTitle: Janaki, a young woman, loves Manu Pratap Singh but is forced to marry Dhirendra, a police inspector. However, when she gets kidnapped by a man, who tries to rape her, Manu saves her in time.

title: Satyakam
subTitle: Satyapriya Acharya, a guiltridden idealist, marries Ranjana, after failing to rescue her from being raped by his employer. However, conflict ensues as he is unable to accept her or her child completely.

title: Satyakam
subTitle: Satyapriya Acharya, a guiltridden idealist, marries Ranjana, after failing to rescue her from being raped by his employer. However, conflict ensues as he is unable to accept her or her child completely.

title: Aap To Aise Na The
subTitle: Vijay, who owns a furniture store, is in love with Varsha. However, Vijay's life takes a drastic turn when she decides to marry his friend Vikram, a rich man, who promises her a better life.

subTitle: Taking advantage of her trusting nature, an unprincipled man seduces a village maiden, only to desert her in her time of need.

title: Shikar
subTitle: A man is killed when he tries to molest a girl. She absconds with the police on her trail and meets a man who tries to help her find the real murderer.

subTitle: When Ajit, a former prisoner, learns of Jabbar who is terrorising the people of his village, he decides to stand up against him. However, things take a turn when Jabbar abducts Ajit's lover.

subTitle: Ashok, a salesman, is in love with Ashoo and wants to marry her. However, things take a turn when his brother kidnaps Ashoo.

title: Dil Ne Phir Yaad Kiya

title: Chandan Ka Palna
subTitle: Ajit's perfect marriage to Shobha turns upside down after she starts behaving strangely with him and his mother, leading to a disturbed life.

title: Anita
subTitle: When Anita commits suicide, Neeraj suspects foul play and decides to investigate the truth. However, things take a turn when he starts seeing Anita everywhere.

subTitle: Rajesh, an apolitical poet, is in love with Kamini and leads a peaceful life. However, when his brother is killed by the British government, he decides to become a revolutionary and joins the freedom struggle.

title: Teri Meherbaniyan

title: Sandwich Double Trouble
